{"tid":16902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"購物狂晒野區，大家講下今日買左d乜～","createTime":"2016-12-01T15:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T15:33:07.000Z","uid":7593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13ee15c20dc4f1c5570ae67c907036c8ee5af1d7","tid":16902,"uid":7593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:33:07.000Z","msg":"我係個購物狂，乜都鍾意買。係有目標之後，都會選擇自己覺得最好嘅牌子同型號去買（當然我好窮，但我買得起我都會買）。就算一條usb線，定係買樓住，我都好鍾意去做功課，務求買到最好最平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係做功課到買嘅時間入面，我會覺得學到野，好有滿足感，唔知有冇人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係依家年齡大左，唔可以乜都買，所以想睇下人地買乜都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己又可以識多樣野，分享下別人買野嘅喜悅。<br />\n<br />\n講左咁多，呢個係呢兩日買嘅～<br />\n<br />\n筆一支<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/233158_248c04b67a6bd2297ed39cfcfaffc8aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F233158_248c04b67a6bd2297ed39cfcfaffc8aa.jpg&h=439f9fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSpeaker 一隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/233303_b9b5149d0da001f6f610c0994486c7e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F233303_b9b5149d0da001f6f610c0994486c7e6.jpg&h=5177f37f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}